{"tid":636824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商經局：毋須改現有郵筒英殖徽號","createTime":"2018-04-21T09:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T09:28:32.000Z","uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"34da00263e65505e0971c1ade4d5787fc24ab43b","tid":636824,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"商經局：毋須改現有郵筒英殖徽號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180420/s00046/b603c398f96fbcac05da741e073609bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180420%2Fs00046%2Fb603c398f96fbcac05da741e073609bf.jpg&h=aa9de73d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為中環遮打道皇后像廣場、編號239嘅郵筒，上面有蘇格蘭皇冠徽號，係全港獨有。（資料圖片）<br />\n圖1之1 - 圖為中環遮打道皇后像廣場、編號239嘅郵筒，上面有蘇格蘭皇冠 . . . . . . （資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】Emily記得本報兩年幾前報道過，香港郵政話舊郵筒展示皇冠標記或者唔同年代嘅英國王室徽號「並不合宜」，所以決定要遮住標記或徽號，又會喺庫存揀唔同款嘅舊郵筒，擺喺歷史建築物內，作為郵政文物畀市民睇，結果惹嚟「去殖化」爭議。至今呢啲措施一直未有時間表，最近商經局書面覆咗立法會議員毛孟靜，話就保育舊郵筒收到唔同持份者意見，研究並充分考慮後，認為毋須更改現有舊郵筒嘅標記或徽號。<br />\n<br />\n長春社嘅facebook設立嘅「香港舊郵筒」專頁噚日公布咗呢個消息，話證明當年大家嘅努力冇白費，希望政府汲取教訓，唔好有意無意又消滅香港僅餘嘅歷史文物喇，其實僅存嘅59個舊郵筒好有歷史價值，所以唔好「強迫佢哋退役」，如果有損毁，政府應該主動修復。"},{"pid":"e8fee47cb6cacfd8fe67d023a6224b24e1d44f59","tid":636824,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"油返紅色先啦"},{"pid":"0609adeb55190f1d0bd66253e67dddd64b7a857e","tid":636824,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e8fee47cb6cacfd8fe67d023a6224b24e1d44f59","tid":636824,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"油返紅色先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:17:18.000Z","msg":"??????????????<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Flag_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party_%28Pre-1996%29.svg/320px-Flag_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party_%28Pre-1996%29.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fb%2Fb9%2FFlag_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party_%2528Pre-1996%2529.svg%2F320px-Flag_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party_%2528Pre-1996%2529.svg.png&h=2fa1c860&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2f3c3583f7d41a70130fc174fa178149b203273","tid":636824,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"中國唔掂就割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bcfaad2e9b2f4f9713dda7a6f4f0de79227ae2","tid":636824,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8fee47cb6cacfd8fe67d023a6224b24e1d44f59","tid":636824,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"油返紅色先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:19:02.000Z","msg":"紅郵筒，真威風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83438acb9910979318854819513518ea4404241","tid":636824,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0609adeb55190f1d0bd66253e67dddd64b7a857e","tid":636824,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e8fee47cb6cacfd8fe67d023a6224b24e1d44f59","tid":636824,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:12:34.000Z","msg":"油返紅色先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:17:18.000Z","msg":"??????????????<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Flag_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party_%28Pre-1996%29.svg/320px-Flag_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party_%28Pre-1996%29.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fb%2Fb9%2FFlag_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party_%2528Pre-1996%2529.svg%2F320px-Flag_of_the_Chinese_Communist_Party_%2528Pre-1996%2529.svg.png&h=2fa1c860&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:28:32.000Z","msg":"死返去做功課啦小學雞"}]}